        Changelog
        ---------
        
        Unreleased
        ~~~~~~~~~~
        0.0.2 (2015-08-28)
        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        
        - Use hstore for tags.
          [msom]
        
        - Filter for current occurrences by default.
          [msom]
        
        - Add autoclean option to add event function.
          [msom]
        
        - Add by_id method for event collections.
          [msom]
        
        - Automatically remove old initiated events.
          [msom]
        
        0.0.1 (2015-08-20)
        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        
        - Initial Release
        
